headline: 3 Services Stocks Worth Your Attention
summary: Business services providers use their specialized expertise to help enterprises streamline operations and cut costs. But cutbacks in corporate spending and the threat of new AI products have kept sentiment in check, and over the past six months, the industry has tumbled by 2.1%. This performance was disappointing since the S&P 500 climbed 5.4%.
